</ul>
</li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-4"><a href="#Golden_Age_.28late_1980s.E2.80.93early_1990s.29"><span class="tocnumber">2</span> <span class="toctext">Golden Age (late 1980s–early 1990s)</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-5"><a href="#Decline_.28mid-1990s.29"><span class="tocnumber">3</span> <span class="toctext">Decline (mid-1990s)</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-6"><a href="#North_American_computer_RPGs_.28late_1990s.29"><span class="tocnumber">4</span> <span class="toctext">North American computer RPGs (late 1990s)</span></a>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-7"><a href="#Diablo_and_action_RPGs"><span class="tocnumber">4.1</span> <span class="toctext"><i>Diablo</i> and action RPGs</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-8"><a href="#Interplay.2C_BioWare.2C_and_Black_Isle"><span class="tocnumber">4.2</span> <span class="toctext">Interplay, BioWare, and Black Isle</span></a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-9"><a href="#Early_21st_century_.282000s.E2.80.93present.29"><span class="tocnumber">5</span> <span class="toctext">Early 21st century (2000s–present)</span></a>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-10"><a href="#Bethesda"><span class="tocnumber">5.1</span> <span class="toctext">Bethesda</span></a></li>
